ClearSky is a lightweight and responsive weather forecasting web application designed to provide users with real-time weather updates for any location worldwide. 
Developed using pure JavaScript, HTML, and CSS, the app fetches live data from a weather API and displays key information such as temperature, humidity, wind speed, and weather conditions through a clean and intuitive interface.
With a focus on performance and usability, 
